#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:101
msgid "ptool.str.split"
msgstr "ptool.str.split"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:103
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:103"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:105
msgid ""
"`ptool.str.split(s, sep[, options])` splits a string by a non-empty "
"separator."
msgstr "`ptool.str.split(s, sep[, options])` は、空でない区切り文字で文字列を 分割し"
"ます。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:107
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:107"
msgid "`s` (string, required): The input string."
msgstr "`s` (string, 必須): 入力文字列。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:108
msgid "`sep` (string, required): The separator. Empty strings are not allowed."
msgstr "`sep` (string, 必須): 区切り文字。空文字列は使えません。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:109
msgid "`options` (table, optional): Split options. Supported fields:"
msgstr "`options` (table, 任意): 分割オプション。サポートされるフィールド:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:109
msgid ""
"`trim` (boolean, optional): Whether to trim each piece before returning it. "
"Defaults to `false`."
msgstr "`trim` (boolean, 任意): 返す前に各要素をトリムするかどうか。 デフォルトは "
"`false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:109
msgid ""
"`skip_empty` (boolean, optional): Whether to remove empty pieces after "
"optional trimming. Defaults to `false`."
msgstr "`skip_empty` (boolean, 任意): トリム後に空要素を取り除くかどうか。 デフォルト"
"は `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:114
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:114"
msgid "Returns: `string[]`."
msgstr "戻り値: `string[]`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:116
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:116"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "挙動:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:118
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:118"
msgid "Unknown option names or invalid option value types raise an error."
msgstr "未知のオプション名や不正な値型はエラーになります。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:119
msgid ""
"`skip_empty = true` is applied after `trim`, so whitespace-only pieces can "
"be removed when both are enabled."
msgstr "`skip_empty = true` は `trim` の後に適用されるため、両方を有効にすると 空白だ"
"けの要素も除去できます。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:131
msgid "ptool.str.split_lines"
msgstr "ptool.str.split_lines"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:133
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:133"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:135
msgid "`ptool.str.split_lines(s[, options])` splits a string into lines."
msgstr "`ptool.str.split_lines(s[, options])` は文字列を行に分割します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:137
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:137"
msgid "`s` (string, required): The input string."
msgstr "`s` (string, 必須): 入力文字列。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:138
msgid "`options` (table, optional): Line-splitting options. Supported fields:"
msgstr "`options` (table, 任意): 行分割オプション。サポートされるフィールド:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:138
msgid ""
"`keep_ending` (boolean, optional): Whether to keep line endings (`\\n"
"`, `\\r\\n"
"`, or `\\r`) in returned items. Defaults to `false`."
msgstr ""
"`keep_ending` (boolean, 任意): 行末 (`\\n"
"`, `\\r\\n"
"`, `\\r`) を返す要素に 残すかどうか。デフォルトは `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:138
msgid ""
"`skip_empty` (boolean, optional): Whether to remove empty lines. Defaults to "
"`false`."
msgstr "`skip_empty` (boolean, 任意): 空行を取り除くかどうか。デフォルトは `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:143
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:143"
msgid "Returns: `string[]`."
msgstr "戻り値: `string[]`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:145
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:145"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "挙動:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:147
msgid ""
"Supports Unix (`\\n"
"`) and Windows (`\\r\\n"
"`) line endings, and also lone `\\r`."
msgstr ""
"Unix (`\\n"
"`) と Windows (`\\r\\n"
"`) の行末、および単独の `\\r` を サポートします。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:148
msgid ""
"When `skip_empty = true`, a line containing only a line ending is treated as "
"empty and is removed."
msgstr "`skip_empty = true` のとき、行末だけを含む行は空行として扱われて 取り除かれま"
"す。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:150
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:150"
msgid "Unknown option names or invalid option value types raise an error."
msgstr "未知のオプション名や不正な値型はエラーになります。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/str.md:160
msgid "ptool.str.join"
msgstr "ptool.str.join"

